data.description: **Seller now offering 2500.00 buyer use as you choose credit!**Welcome to 113 Berkshire drive in the heart of Havelock! Just minutes from both the front and back gates to MCAS Cherry Point! This show stopper has been well maintained and is MOVE IN READY! Featuring solar panels that transfer at no additional cost (with warranty) to the new homeowner and can save up to hundreds per month in energy costs! This home also has an assumable VA loan for eligible buyers! Sitting on a great sized lot with fenced in back yard, this 3 bedroom, 2 full bathroom house with garage will check all of your boxes! As you pull up you will fall in love with the beautiful porch that overlooks the front yard. Step inside and be greeted by beautiful LVP flooring throughout. The large living room featuring a wood burning fireplace is perfect for entertaining guests! Stunning kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, window that overlooks the back yard, expansive walk in pantry, and full laundry room! Bathrooms have been updated and are easy to maintain! Fenced in backyard is great for pets enjoying the outdoors! Sit on the deck and drink your morning coffee or on chilly fall evenings enjoy a fire around the firepit! Schedule your tour today! This house will not last long!
